formalpara.title: Internal help for this function in Asterisk 1.4:

para.screen:
-= Info about function 'CHECK_MD5' =-
[Syntax] CHECK_MD5(<digest>,<data>)
[Synopsis] Checks an MD5 digest
[Description] Returns 1 on a match, 0 otherwise
